{"tid":217880,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人試過遮陌生人","createTime":"2017-04-26T06:23:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-26T12:49:12.000Z","uid":98662,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8d5368394a2dc9ea60fe2d8a09c9eccaff1b234f","tid":217880,"uid":98662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T06:23:45.000Z","msg":"會唔會好老尷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"210e6e0b6fbf271107897abc748c2cf6a6fe5f72","tid":217880,"uid":69525,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T06:24:27.000Z","msg":"有比人遮 但無遮過人<br />\n多數自己都無帶遮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b7627f159b9cc12ebcf6a0645fd9c7f19aed9e0","tid":217880,"uid":98662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T08:23:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有比人遮 但無遮過人<br />\n多數自己都無帶遮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我遮過d拎膠袋笠住個頭嘅呀婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e156d39203ca5841229785dd09e01e90f091de3","tid":217880,"uid":84895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T08:25:24.000Z","msg":"男遮男好老尷 遮女就傾下計咁<br />\n利申 男女都遮過"},{"pid":"f8b9dee80e792c4c5b454d30509c8d07e4c3a0aa","tid":217880,"uid":4705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T08:27:14.000Z","msg":"有遮過<br />\n有時等車個陣見到隔離有人冇遮會遮埋<br />\n男女都遮過<br />\n女仔會好傾啲<br />\n<br />\n有次試過個男仔話好柒 要個女仔遮<br />\n問我可唔可以比把遮佢拎感覺好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38339f7a744b0d11e4966383971b45ad1468fbce","tid":217880,"uid":111381,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T08:27:36.000Z","msg":"試過落好大雨 係個輕鐵站到出唔到去<br />\n又無帶遮 點知等等下有個女仔同我講<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：不如遮埋你<br />\n之後真係一齊行住走  雖然濕鬼哂<br />\n但都估唔到有咁好既人 好想同佢講翻句多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25d97d3a651f05bd0a6f8f812992ad96191d2590","tid":217880,"uid":111187,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T08:33:43.000Z","msg":"有啊 個陣真係好大雨<br />\n個姨姨冇遮又焗住等過馬路<br />\n所以遮埋佢"},{"pid":"2fd52cb7cadca86ff032c397dede22c6548973e4","tid":217880,"uid":37664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T08:39:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過落好大雨 係個輕鐵站到出唔到去<br />\n又無帶遮 點知等等下有個女仔同我講<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：不如遮埋你<br />\n之後真係一齊行住走  雖然濕鬼哂<br />\n但都估唔到有咁好既人 好想同佢講翻句多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌人地遮完你唔係第一下就要講唔該啦咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即係由人地遮你到分開，你一粒聲都冇出過?"},{"pid":"ab8be29c13db36f31583321ea9f4d9469a7760b5","tid":217880,"uid":77054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T08:47:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>試過落好大雨 係個輕鐵站到出唔到去<br />\n又無帶遮 點知等等下有個女仔同我講<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：不如遮埋你<br />\n之後真係一齊行住走  雖然濕鬼哂<br />\n但都估唔到有咁好既人 好想同佢講翻句多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌人地遮完你唔係第一下就要講唔該啦咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即係由人地遮你到分開，你一粒聲都冇出過?</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c18f2acdbaf195995e46907ca9c0a85f554604c","tid":217880,"uid":27745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T08:51:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過落好大雨 係個輕鐵站到出唔到去<br />\n又無帶遮 點知等等下有個女仔同我講<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：不如遮埋你<br />\n之後真係一齊行住走  雖然濕鬼哂<br />\n但都估唔到有咁好既人 好想同佢講翻句多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔該/多謝都冇句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  90後"},{"pid":"4935fe669ac2dc08af9da7020b40778dd5726853","tid":217880,"uid":63867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T09:02:09.000Z","msg":"有 幫得就幫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d74d17a1123d37bec9e544a5a966ea063d3e24af","tid":217880,"uid":105425,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T09:03:52.000Z","msg":"好多年前試過好大雨<br />\n直接俾咗把遮對情侶<br />\n自己濕得好緊要<br />\n<br />\nP.S.: 唔會再咁on9"},{"pid":"259d5719095478440c83f943372d8e782cce33eb","tid":217880,"uid":105833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T09:05:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>試過落好大雨 係個輕鐵站到出唔到去<br />\n又無帶遮 點知等等下有個女仔同我講<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：不如遮埋你<br />\n之後真係一齊行住走  雖然濕鬼哂<br />\n但都估唔到有咁好既人 好想同佢講翻句多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔該/多謝都冇句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  90後</blockquote><br />\n遮過幾次男仔<br />\n全部多謝都冇仲西面<br />\n唔知想點"},{"pid":"10d79dee0942a77e0992987376c2280f724164b0","tid":217880,"uid":98645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T09:06:43.000Z","msg":"直接比左把遮人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"825b2538cdb6fb6c42b2e0a83623c54db344d496","tid":217880,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T09:08:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>試過落好大雨 係個輕鐵站到出唔到去<br />\n又無帶遮 點知等等下有個女仔同我講<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：不如遮埋你<br />\n之後真係一齊行住走  雖然濕鬼哂<br />\n但都估唔到有咁好既人 好想同佢講翻句多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔該/多謝都冇句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  90後</blockquote><br />\n遮過幾次男仔<br />\n全部多謝都冇仲西面<br />\n唔知想點</blockquote><br />\n咁耐都無人遮過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"363432e55983b4c60d8a6eee1b39376801e9a453","tid":217880,"uid":72567,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T09:11:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8980e8eb3637e8028b889b524643bd513de33ce8","tid":217880,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T09:50:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你 。。。。mk!!"},{"pid":"e11a1678dab460c9e26887853430f3914711dfdb","tid":217880,"uid":2762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T09:56:03.000Z","msg":"遮人唔尷尬 最尷尬係你唔知要遮到幾時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n假設你遮完對方過馬路 但你行左 佢行右 <br />\n個陣走又唔係 唔走又唔知佢會去到邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb2345b2c8d94e355649592b08da7caa12fc7674","tid":217880,"uid":72567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T09:57:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>遮人唔尷尬 最尷尬係你唔知要遮到幾時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n假設你遮完對方過馬路 但你行左 佢行右 <br />\n個陣走又唔係 唔走又唔知佢會去到邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以開場白係，你去邊呀，不如我遮埋你"},{"pid":"dc2a1262b1c42f97041458056e5f8a796cbfcd00","tid":217880,"uid":27509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T10:09:21.000Z","msg":"遮過個女仔<br />\n其實都幾尷尬無乜好講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bfcb61b087a3b274ce3dbd9a22d9b9c76fedb94","tid":217880,"uid":81737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T10:11:34.000Z","msg":"有 見靚女咪遮埋 <br />\n全程冇講野幾想尷<br />\n<br />\n想拎電話又驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12a8917a3e8f76d1a0ac781578bd39a4f6e0d8f0","tid":217880,"uid":76804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T10:11:47.000Z","msg":"試過一次離遠見到有個女仔 企係室內(巴士站)等好耐<br />\n出面好大雨 之後佢衝左出去<br />\n我急步行過去遮佢<br />\n之後問佢去邊<br />\n佢指前面其中一個方向<br />\n我無再問 繼續遮佢<br />\n點知原來我地都係住同一棟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n試過搭巴士 無野遮 突然大雨<br />\n前面個呀伯無擔遮 我就遮埋佢<br />\n<br />\n最近試過遮個女仔<br />\n問佢去邊佢話是旦無所謂 之後遮完一個路口就話唔該曬 就跑走左"},{"pid":"041f21bba6ab626bb62b64a897e477f21c2e90c7","tid":217880,"uid":68641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T10:17:42.000Z","msg":"有<br />\n會<br />\n但見佢濕又唔係太好"},{"pid":"2884aaa137965ff35b351fec7a5056a9a600378d","tid":217880,"uid":44678,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T10:19:14.000Z","msg":"試過放lunch,見個女仔係樓下好似好心急想走又無遮，果陣紅雨。<br />\n我搭𨋢上到去食飯果層，唔忍心再落去直接比把遮佢叫佢走，佢有講佢係樓上間日本餐廳做，叫我得閒去拎返，但唔敢去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後自己無遮要打比同事接<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f43b0535e8ea82aa1112bb6142e1e801237abbfb","tid":217880,"uid":44423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T10:58:55.000Z","msg":"會遮 把遮一定要斜去對方個邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}